0received%20on%20the%20remote%20side.%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%2F%20%40dev%20Struct%20representing%20OFT%20fee%20details.%5Cn%2F%2F%2F%20%40dev%20Future%20proof%20mechanism%20to%20provide%20a%20standardized%20way%20to%20communicate%20fees%20to%20things%20like%20a%20UI.%5Cnstruct%20OFTFeeDetail%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20int256%20feeAmount%3B%20%2F%2F%20Amount%20of%20the%20fee.%5Cn%20%20%20%20string%20description%3B%20%2F%2F%20Description%20of%20the%20fee.%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%2F%20%40title%20IOFTCore%5Cn%2F%2F%2F%20%40author%20Forked%20from%5Cn%2F%2F%2F%20https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FLayerZero-Labs%2FLayerZero-v2%2Fblob%2Fmain%2Fpackages%2Flayerzero-v2%2Fevm%2Foapp%2Fcontracts%2Foft%2FIOFT.sol%5Cn%2F%2F%2F%20%40dev%20Modifications%20made%20by%20Cooper%20Labs.%20Removing%20sharedDecimals%2FdecimalConversionRate%20feature.%5Cn%2F%2F%2F%20%40dev%20Interface%20for%20the%20OftChain%20%28OFT%29%20token.%5Cn%2F%2F%2F%20%40dev%20Does%20not%20inherit%20ERC20%20to%20accommodate%20usage%20by%20OFTAdapter%20as%20well.%5Cn%2F%2F%2F%20%40dev%20This%20specific%20interface%20ID%20is%20%270x18fb6cf8%27.%5Cninterface%20IOFT%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20error%20SlippageExceeded%28uint256%20amount%2C%20uint256%20minAmount%29%3B%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20Events%5Cn%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20GUID%20of%20the%20OFT%20message.%5Cn%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20Destination%20Endpoint%20ID.%5Cn%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20Address%20of%20the%20sender%20on%20the%20src%20chain.%5Cn%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20Amount%20of%20tokens%20sent.%5Cn%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20Amount%20of%20tokens%20received.%5Cn%20%20%20%20event%20OFTSent%28%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20bytes32%20indexed%20guid%2C%20uint32%20dstEid%2C%20address%20indexed%20fromAddress%2C%20uint256%20amountSent%2C%20uint256%20amountReceived%5Cn%20%20%20%20%29%3B%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20GUID%20of%20the%20OFT%20message.%5Cn%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20Source%20Endpoint%20ID.%5Cn%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20Address%20of%20the%20recipient%20on%20the%20dst%20chain.%5Cn%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20Amount%20of%20tokens%20